name: Become One with Universe (animated version)
description: Human must position his Manah or his heart in a state of "Manembah". Manembah is "practice" or human consciousness in patience who accepts sincerely with what is happening in the universe or Jagad Ageng. The manembah depicted in the work is the position of the hands of Anjali Mudra which is done in his real form and in his mind. Humans dwell to meditate, touch and understand the practice of the Mandala of the Universe as Jagad Ageng and become in harmony and unified in the Universe
